item.description:
Join us as we plan for Tax Day.  Hear about important legislation pending on Beacon Hill regarding illegal immigration.  State Representative Daniel Webster will be speaking about his legislation that seeks to scale back the disastrous economic effects of pervasive illegal immigration to MA.

 

The pizza is tops.  Bring a friend and join the movement!
